00:15:16,987 --> 00:15:18,750
God, she's annoying.

241
00:15:20,057 --> 00:15:21,854
At least you're not a third nipple.

242
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:24,791
Jake, why don't you go in the kitchen

243
00:15:24,895 --> 00:15:27,830
