that you understand how vulnerable he is.

251
00:16:00,664 --> 00:16:03,258
You don't think I'm vulnerable, too?

252
00:16:03,534 --> 00:16:05,126
Maybe you haven't noticed, Charlie,

253
00:16:05,202 --> 00:16:07,932
but I'm wrapped tighter
than an airport sandwich.

254
00:16:08,839 --> 00:16:12,502
