- He did it with me.

260
00:16:31,795 --> 00:16:33,695
You really care about him, don't you?

261
00:16:35,699 --> 00:16:36,825
Yes.

262
00:16:37,935 --> 00:16:39,960
You're a great guy, Charlie.

263
00:16:46,843 --> 00:16:49,141
Great guy and a kiss on the cheek.

264
00:16:50,547 --> 00:16:52,811
Why doesn't she just kick me in the balls?

