so that they're emotional...

274
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:24,704
No, not always.

275
00:17:31,655 --> 00:17:35,250
Listen, Frankie, I was thinking.

276
00:17:35,926 --> 00:17:39,828
We get along so well,
and our kids get along,

277
00:17:39,896 --> 00:17:42,831
and since neither one of us
really has our own place...

278
00:17:42,899 --> 00:17:43,923
Alan.

279
00:17:48,905 --> 00:17:50,236
Absolutely not.

280
00:17:52,442 --> 00:17:54,239
- But...
- No. My life is such a mess,

281
00:17:54,344 --> 00:17:56,744
