back together again.

292
00:18:36,553 --> 00:18:39,317
Yeah, no. That makes sense. Sure.

293
00:18:41,391 --> 00:18:44,758
- I'm sorry.
- No. You're doing the right thing.

294
00:18:45,829 --> 00:18:49,094
