305
00:19:42,886 --> 00:19:45,116
You know,
this doesn't have to be goodbye forever.

306
00:19:47,576 --> 00:19:49,908
Once we get all settled,
you can come visit us.

307
00:19:51,146 --> 00:19:52,170
Sure.

308
00:20:07,829 --> 00:20:10,093
Bye.

309
00:20:30,352 --> 00:20:31,717
Here, I'm running late.

310
00:20:45,066 --> 00:20:49,025
- It's tough seeing her go, isn't it?
